txt.en: Hurry and travel to Bree-town to experience this year's annual celebration. Hurry and join the festivities!

Every year in the spring, the Anniversary Event takes place to celebrate a very special occasion.  Come and join the festivities in Bree-town to help mark this milestone with fireworks and good-cheer!
